{"tid":634490,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"終於有日本媒體報導成龍的真面目，點可以唔幫手宣傳。👏👏👏","createTime":"2018-04-19T09:20:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T09:48:09.000Z","uid":22675,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fd299d4582b6cbacf12b3f6e4e14b4b917360b1e","tid":634490,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T09:20:13.000Z","msg":"終於有日本媒體報導此人的真面目，點可以唔幫手宣傳。👏👏👏<br />\n<br />\n台灣旅日作家兼時事評論員黃文雄，就早前的香港電影金像獎頒獎典禮中黃秋生的發言，帶出香港電影界以至香港人對此人的反感。從近期「沒有香港電影、只有中國電影」，到「中國人是要被管的」，再申延至民進黨第一次執政時說過「不會去台灣」...等等的言行，都有清晰的解說。<br />\n<br />\n文中提到在沒有創作言論自由的中國，藝人被錢收買，創作「官製文化」，成為統戰機器一部份。有人更當上政協之位，形容他是「中国の犬」。<br />\n不過文中並未提及此人的私德問題，否則會更精彩。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/samanthaselect/posts/1671885639569972\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsamanthaselect%2Fposts%2F1671885639569972&d=EInaWhk2nI5nG1o40UuM1i7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=5334d555\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/samanthaselect/posts/1671885639569972</a>"},{"pid":"a7b3fde912e45a6af8a6ea2854c50e0be47aef43","tid":634490,"uid":104171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T09:24:11.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"3c761c5f7c2e5671fc474e38351bc66440c58c0f","tid":634490,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T09:37:37.000Z","msg":"遮乜野呀，係人都知你係雞黎架啦"},{"pid":"072a8f46a896be37128ce97c43d3ce46a6aeb89c","tid":634490,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c761c5f7c2e5671fc474e38351bc66440c58c0f","tid":634490,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T09:37:37.000Z","msg":"遮乜野呀，係人都知你係雞黎架啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T09:48:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}